msgid ""
"Now that our boat is ready, we need to create the tour itself. Still in the Appointments app, we select <strong>Appointments</strong> and click on <strong>New</strong>. There we set the <strong>Duration</strong>,\n"
"            <strong>Schedule</strong> and assign the relevant <strong>Resources</strong>.<br/>\n"
